Sanctuary
Discworld ritual help
Sanctuary

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
Sanctuary - Allows escape from danger by moving priest to a safe 
place.
.EP

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
Sanctuary asks your god to remove you from danger, by shifting you
to a safe and impervious area for the duration of the ritual, using
your skill in defensive rituals. A prayer book and holy incense are 
both required in the working of this ritual.
.EP
